{% block content %}
    <section id="overview">
        <div class="bg-white">
            <div class="container py-8 lg:py-14">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl">
                    In the dynamic world of business, possessing a well-crafted and
                    clearly defined strategy is crucial for outpacing competitors and
                    achieving lasting success. For companies operating within
                    Indonesia, a market characterized by its unique set of challenges
                    and opportunities, the importance of strategic planning is even
